sequenceDiagram
  actor U as User
  participant SPA as React SPA
  participant API as AuthController
  participant DB as SQL Server
  U->>SPA: Submit email/password
  SPA->>API: POST /api/auth/login
  API->>DB: Load user + roles + status
  alt invalid or disabled
    API-->>SPA: 401/403
  else valid
    API-->>SPA: JWT + safe user DTO
    SPA->>SPA: Persist token in memory/storage
  end
